N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 332.2 - Transmission of information

State Regulations

As the applications are received the division shall
transmit to the appropriate board of elections the name, residence and military
addresses of each military voter, as shall be ascertained by the division from
the applications received by the division. The board of elections shall enter
the same in the register of voters and/or on the registration
records. Notes
